<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Tabu is the perfect place to meet other like-minded adults who are interested in the swinging lifestyle. We have gone to painstaking lengths to provide our members with a clean, fun, and safe environment to interact socially, casually, or sexually. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Tabu Lifestyle Club is a private membership Social Club that caters to mature, open-minded adults. Tabu is also a BYOB club, which means "bring your own bottle" and we encourage you to do so. We will provide all set ups at no additional charge. </span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="works" class="sppb-section"><div class="sppb-row-container"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-sm-12  " id="column-wrap-id-1488854284"><div id="column-id-1488854284" class="sppb-column "><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1496772251885" class="sppb-addon-wrapper  addon-root-text-block"><div id="sppb-addon-1496772251885" class="clearfix  "><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-text-block "><h3 class="sppb-addon-title">TABU UPCOMING EVENTS</h3><div class="sppb-addon-content  "><p><i class="fa fa-fire" style="font-size: 30px; color: #ff0000;" aria-hidden="true"></i>   <span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 14pt;">GET READY FOR A HOT WEEKEND</span></p></div></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1504534656812" class="sppb-addon-wrapper  addon-root-empty-space"><div id="sppb-addon-1504534656812" class="clearfix  "><div class="sppb-empty-space  clearfix"></div></div></div><div id="sppb-addon-wrapper-1504534656803" class="sppb-addon-wrapper  addon-root-module"><div id="sppb-addon-1504534656803" class="clearfix  "><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-module "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="moduletable ">
